features: 36" Height Versatile and Practical Coffee Bar: There are endless possibilities with this accent storage cabinet to maximize your space. A 29 inch wide spacious cabinet top offer a perfect place to set up coffee maker and cups, while 3 lower adjustable display shelves offer plenty of storage space for your living room, kitchen, bedroom or dining room essentials to meet the needs of storage items of different sizes.

Dimensions and Material: 29.53"W x 13.39"D x 36.00"H. Crafted from high-quality MDF board with rustic oak wood grain finished that adds farmhouse touch to your home. We also use powder coating to seal up the steel and the metal of this storage cabinet won’t rust over time.

Not Wobbles: Thanks to heavy duty metal frame and support tube under bottom shelf, the bar cabinet stands quit stable. We also provide anti-tip device, you can mount this bar cart to the wall to avoid unexpected tipping. 4pcs pre-assembled plastic pads protect your wood floor from scratching.

High Weight Capacity Rustic Cabinet: The cabinet top can bear 300 lbs home supplies and each shelf hold up to 100 lbs. With its ample storage space and strong weight capacity, you can display everything you need close at hand.

Easy to Assemble: This wood metal small buffet takes around 25 minutes to assemble. Necessary hardware and instruction are provided. If you have any questions with our product, please do not hesitate to let us know. We always reply within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This cabinet is the perfect size for a bar, and I love the dark wood accents. It took 2 people a little less than an hour to put together, and it was not difficult at all because the directions were clear. There were a lot of extra parts including a replacement magnet for the doors, which was a nice touch. I was happy to see the shelf heights were adjustable since I have some odd sized bottles. Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a very nice little cabinet. The size is perfect for the space we wanted to put it in and the quality of the product is nicer that I expected. It appears to be very sturdy. No scratches or anything. The pieces were very well packaged. The instructions were pretty easy to follow. We did have a little trouble getting the right door to line up but I reached out to the seller and they responded right away with additional instructions and it worked perfectly. They were very responsive. Happy with the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Classy and Useful!
reviews.reviewText: This is my coffee bar and I absolutely love it. It is very sturdy and easy to assemble. I love how the entire shelf area is enclosed, it is perfect to keep the kitties out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Excellent addition to our kitchen as extension to our coffee bar! Easy to put together with included instructions and sturdy. Mesh door had an imperfection and the company was very quick to respond to send out a replacement that arrived in great condition. Overall, very happy with our purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to use as a coffee bar and for kitchen storage and it is serving those purposes well. Assembly was easy and quality is better than I expected.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful! Just as described.Top piece is just particle board, so be careful with spillage- but seems to be pretty sturdy! Shelves are very adjustable, which is nice for odd-shaped items of various sizes (I use it as a liquor cabinet).Box is heavy- be careful! And try to put it together somewhere close to where you want to put it. Will need to shift it around a good bit when putting it together, but I did not find rotating it to be very difficult.No issues putting it together- pretty straightforward process with clear directions, despite being time consuming.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this so much!
reviews.reviewText: This is absolutely perfect!! I kept most of these items in my cupboard above the sink. It freed up all that space! The only part of putting it together was the first screws for the magnetic closers. The holes weren't drilled out all the way. I just put the screws in without the brackets to make the hole. Other than that it was pretty straightforward. It has plenty of space and seems pretty sturdy. It's a perfect size and I have room for more items too. There wasn't any damage and all the parts were there. They even gave me a bag of extra parts. It came with some small tools (Allen wrench, philips screwdriver and flathead) but I used my own. I'd call this an excellent purchase. I'm so happy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Coffee Bar
reviews.reviewText: I love the aesthetic look that this piece of furniture provided for the perfect little space between kitchen and dining room!!! Easy to build, sturdy, correct hardware and markings aligned.
